Ayo.

91
00:05:37,417 --> 00:05:40,250
Orion, kau bawa lembar izinmu?

92
00:05:40,333 --> 00:05:42,417
<i>Aku takut ia akan tanyakan.</i>

93
00:05:43,708 --> 00:05:49,458
Orang tua saya tak mengizinkan.
Ya, mereka tak percaya luar angkasa.

94
