355
00:23:03,542 --> 00:23:05,583
Apa maksudmu "yang lain"?

356
00:23:05,667 --> 00:23:07,375
Entitas malam lainnya.

357
00:23:07,458 --> 00:23:09,083
Tunggu, ada lagi?

358
00:23:09,167 --> 00:23:10,750
KAFE HIGHWAY

